  "input": {
    "passage": "Hello! I am Tom. I see my friend Sam. \"Hello, Sam!\" I say. Sam can play with me, and I am very happy. \"Thank you, Tom,\" Sam says. \"Sorry, I have to go now.\" \"Goodbye, Sam! Please come every day!\"",
    "passageZh": "哈囉！我是湯姆。我看到我的朋友山姆。「哈囉，山姆!」我說。山姆可以跟我玩，我很開心。「謝謝你，湯姆，」山姆說。「對不起，我現在要走了。」「再見，山姆！請每天都來!」",
